      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUCKY VINCENT (2) finished fifth last start, beaten 13 metres at Bendigo over 2150m. Talented and has plenty of upside. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Has the talent to take care of this field. ROCKNROLL WILLOW (6) resumes from a spell of four months after showing some very good form last campaign, the last run being a eighth over 2240m at Melton. Likely to run a big race to kick off this campaign. MEDIA MOGUL (4) last appeared when eighth over 1790m at Ararat five months ago. Expect a better effort to kick off this prep. ONYX (8) won two starts ago then things went wrong last start when he broke and finished 35 metres away in sixth over 2180m at Terang. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Won't find this any harder and he can bounce back.",
